[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    174[0m:[38;5;10m[49m In production, patient data comes from your EHR data lake via Athena queries. Here we define synthetic patients to demonstrate the matching logic. (Use Synthea for realistic synthetic data in development. Never use real PHI.)
